Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:05.93,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}埋藏的感情释放悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:11.52,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,500)}坚定的誓言紧握手心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:26.91,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}一心追求奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:32.08,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}在无尽的黑暗中彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.80,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}若在此停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:42.68,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}就再也看不到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.35,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}今宵亦有明月相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.93,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}虽然还未能吐露真意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.27,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}但心中一直在呐喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:58.24,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}埋藏的感情释放悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:03.37,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}坚定的誓言紧握手心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:08.87,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.58,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.38,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}就能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:20.55,OP2-CN,,0,0,0,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}在那前方的未来
